answer.code:
"My life is now a monotonous" said the fox. I hunt
              chickens ; men hunt me. All
the chickens are just alike, and all the men are just alike.
               And, in consequances, 
I am a little bored. But if you tame me, it will b as if the 
               sun came to shine on 
                      my life.
